<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Experience Certificate</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .letterhead {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .company-address {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .doc-title-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }

        .cert-meta {
            text-align: right;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .cert-meta strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .details-table th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            width: 35%;
        }

        .details-table td {
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .performance-section {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .perf-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        .perf-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .perf-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .verify-note {
            background: #fefce8;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #92400e;
        }

        .verify-note strong {
            color: #78350f;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 48px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .seal-block {
            width: 40%;
        }

        .seal-box {
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 8px;
            height: 72px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .signature-block {
            width: 40%;
        }

        .sig-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            padding-top: 8px;
        }

        .sig-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .sig-role {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="letterhead">
        <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        <div class="company-address">
            {{{companyAddress}}}
            {{#if companyPhone}}<br>{{companyPhone}}{{/if}}
            {{#if companyEmail}} | {{companyEmail}}{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doc-title-wrap">
        <div class="doc-title">EXPERIENCE CERTIFICATE</div>
    </div>

    <div class="cert-meta">
        <strong>Certificate No:</strong> {{#if
        certificateNumber}}{{certificateNumber}}{{else}}EXP/{{currentYear}}/{{employeeId}}{{/if}}<br>
        <strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p class="section-label">To Whom It May Concern</p>

        <p>This is to certify that <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong> was employed with {{companyName}} in the following
            capacity:</p>

        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Employee Name</th>
                <td>{{employeeName}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Position Held</th>
                <td>{{position}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Department</th>
                <td>{{department}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{#if employeeId}}<tr>
                <th>Employee ID</th>
                <td>{{employeeId}}</td>
            </tr>{{/if}}
            <tr>
                <th>Date of Joining</th>
                <td>{{joiningDate}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Date of Relieving</th>
                <td>{{relievingDate}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Total Experience</th>
                <td>{{#if totalExperience}}{{totalExperience}}{{else}}As per employment period{{/if}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="performance-section">
            <div class="perf-title">Work Performance & Conduct</div>
            <p>During the tenure of employment, {{employeeName}} demonstrated exceptional professionalism, dedication,
                and competence. {{#if workDescription}}{{workDescription}}{{else}}The employee consistently met
                performance objectives and maintained high standards of work quality.{{/if}}</p>
            <ul class="perf-list">
                <li>Consistently exceeded performance targets and objectives</li>
                <li>Demonstrated strong leadership and collaborative skills</li>
                <li>Contributed significantly to departmental and organizational goals</li>
                <li>Maintained excellent professional conduct and work ethics</li>
                {{#if achievements}}<li>{{achievements}}</li>{{/if}}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We found {{employeeName}} to be honest, hardworking, reliable, and a person of good character. The employee
            maintained excellent relationships with colleagues, clients, and management throughout the employment
            period.</p>

        {{#if reasonForLeaving}}
        <p><strong>Reason for Leaving:</strong> {{reasonForLeaving}}</p>
        {{/if}}

        <p>We have no hesitation in recommending {{employeeName}} for future employment opportunities and wish them
            success in all future endeavors.</p>

        <div class="verify-note">
            <strong>For Verification:</strong> This certificate can be verified by contacting our HR department at {{#if
            hrEmail}}{{hrEmail}}{{else}}hr@company.com{{/if}} or {{#if hrPhone}}{{hrPhone}}{{else}}+91-XXXXXXXXXX{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="seal-block">
            <div class="section-label">Company Seal</div>
            <div class="seal-box">COMPANY SEAL</div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="sig-label">Authorized Signatory</div>
            <div class="sig-line">
                <div class="sig-name">{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Manager{{/if}}</div>
                <div class="sig-role">{{#if managerTitle}}{{managerTitle}}{{else}}Human Resources
                    Manager{{/if}}<br>{{companyName}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is a system-generated certificate. Valid without signature. {{companyName}}</p>
        {{#if currentDate}}<p>Generated on {{currentDate}}</p>{{/if}}
    </div>
</body>

</html>